14:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekistonda avtofuqarolik javobgarligini majburiy sug'urtalash (OSAGO) barcha transport vositasi egalari uchun majburiy hisoblanadi. OSAGO bazaviy tarifi 65 000 so'mdan boshlanadi va transport vositasi turi, foydalanish hududi, haydovchi staji va «bonus-malus» koeffitsientiga (avariyasiz haydash uchun chegirma) bog'liq."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Hisoblash formulasi: OSAGO narxi = Bazaviy tarif × Kt (hudud) × Ks (staj) × Kbm (bonus-malus) × Km (quvvat). Hududiy koeffitsient (Kt) Toshkent uchun — 1,7; Toshkent viloyati — 1,3; boshqa hududlar — 0,8-1,2. Staj koeffitsienti (Ks): 2 yildan kam — 1,8; 2-5 yil — 1,2; 5-10 yil — 1,0; 10 yildan ortiq — 0,9."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Hisoblash misoli: Toshkentda yengil avtomobil, haydovchi staji 7 yil, 3 yil YTHsiz. Bazaviy tarif: 65 000 so'm. Kt: 1,7. Ks: 1,0. Kbm: 0,85. Narx = 65 000 × 1,7 × 1,0 × 0,85 ≈ 93 925 so'm/yil. Yangi haydovchi uchun (staj <2 yil) Toshkentda: 65 000 × 1,7 × 1,8 × 1,0 ≈ 198 900 so'm."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"OSAGO bo'yicha maksimal sug'urta to'lovlari: hayot va sog'likka zarar uchun — 52 mln so'mgacha; mol-mulkka zarar uchun — 28 mln so'mgacha (umumiy limit 80 mln so'm). Sug'urta hodisasi yuz berganda: YHXni chaqirish, YTH holatlarini qayd etish, 3 ish kuni ichida sug'urta kompaniyasiga murojaat qilish kerak."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"OSAGO polisi 12 oyga rasmiylashtiriladi va sug'urta kompaniyalari ofislarida yoki onlayn sotib olinishi mumkin. OSAGOsiz haydash — ma'muriy huquqbuzarlik (MJtKning 135-1-moddasi): ogohlantirish yoki 0,5 "}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/bhm","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"BHK"}],["$","$1","2",{"children":" jarima (206 000 so'm)."}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 space-y-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-foreground","children":"Ma'lumotnoma va tariflar"}],[["$","div","0",{"className":"overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-border","children":["$","table",null,{"className":"w-full text-sm","children":[["$","caption",null,{"className":"px-4 py-2 text-left font-medium text-foreground bg-muted/50 border-b border-border","children":"Bojxona boji: sm³ uchun ustama (15% yangi / 40% ishlatilgan ustiga)"}],["$","thead",null,{"children":["$","tr",null,{"className":"bg-muted/30","children":[["$","th","0",{"className":"px-4 py-2.5 text-left font-medium text-foreground border-b border-border","children":"Dvigatel hajmi"}],"$L1a"]}]}],"$L1b